

    Rotational Selector Dial – Flick a smooth, tactile dial to toggle between tanks. Each rotation activates the chosen chamber while shutting off the others, ensuring that only one strain is heated at a time.

    Smart Coil Activation – Draw-activated heating engages instantly, providing a smooth, flavorful hit with no preheating required.

    Battery & Oil Synchronization – The internal battery is engineered to match the consumption cycle of all three tanks. Optional USB-C fast charging ensures you never run out of power while oil remains.
